{"type": "article", "id": 8809, "title": "Pirouet 灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-23T07:16:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235128TMp2dFYrfx1aclQo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一款可以通过调节孔径的大小改变灯光的吊灯，这款名为 “Pirouet” 的灯设计上的理念非常简单，就是希望能够注意到孔径的精美，在灯的开关中，看到形状和灯光的双重变化。它的设计甚至有一点像我们在最普通的生日蛋糕里附送的“莲花”蜡烛，而当“蜡烛”180 度上下翻转，通过板块的变化，我们可以轻松营造不同的灯光氛围。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235126SX785Tb2gIKzkirD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235126tTY9BlZIr6nbMsqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235127lsOb2UKuRMZwjx8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235127ioRpc5Vdn1PasUQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235128ClnFwbg80KB3hEd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}